CHOLERA - SRI LANKA (04)
************************
A ProMED-mail post
<http://www.healthnet.org/programs/promed.html>
See Also
Cholera - Sri Lanka 980429222335
Cholera - Sri Lanka (02) 980616224202
Cholera - Sri Lanka (03) 980707211810
Date: Fri, 14 Aug 1998 09:07:40 -0500
Source: Daily News - Lakehouse Sri Lanka August 14
Via: Clyde Markon <docmarkon@worldnet.att.net>

Two cholera patients died on Sunday at the Trincomalee base hospital and
Kantale district hospital. According to health authorities the patient who
died at the Trincomalee hospital is from Alles Garden and the patient from
Kantale has developed purging after he returned from a pilgrimage to
Kataragama. Up to now seven cholera patients have died in Trincomalee
district. In the meantime a report from Vanni states that there are 20
cholera patients warded at the Mallawi rural hospital.
